This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of natural language processing (cs.CL) as it focuses on evaluating the quality of sentence representations. The paper also uses machine learning techniques to train and evaluate the embeddings, which suggests that it could also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
